nodes.text: Tanner Cadaman was a Human male senator who represented Feenix in the Galactic Senate of the Republic during the Clone Wars. In 19 BBY, he was also a member of the Delegation of 2000.

Shortly after the formation of the Galactic Empire, Cadaman and sixty-two other Senators of the Delegation, including Ivor Drake, Shea Sadashassa, Streamdrinker, Fang Zar and Grebleips, were arrested as supporters of the so-called Jedi Rebellion.
